data.description: This cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom mobile home on a permanent foundation is your ticket to a peaceful retreat on 9.45 acres of gorgeous land. Sitting atop a hill, it offers 1424 square feet of comfort with fresh paint and new flooring that keeps things stylish yet homey. Step onto the spacious back deck to enjoy the stunning views and open space – it's perfect for outdoor fun or just chilling. The entire property is fenced and cross-fenced, so you've got endless possibilities – whether you're dreaming of a hobby farm, simpler living, or just spreading out. And don't forget the two outbuildings, including a roomy 30x40 structure, ready for storage, tinkering, or creative projects. Only 7 minutes away from Sugarloaf Marina on Greers Ferry Lake, this peaceful paradise won't stick around for long. Make it yours – set up a showing today!
